column5: Walk The Plank Mateeee  Thank God it's bbq season again.  What did you guys cook up this weekend?  Decided to pick up some fresh fillets and 'cue up my favourite dish tonight:

Everybody was too busy last night feeding to take any pics. On the menu was a generous mound of walleye, perch and smelt, served up with sides of fresh buns, sausage, beans, salsa and smoky fries. Topped off with trifle and apple pie. Washed down with liberal quantities of a strange amber beverage I'm not too familiar with  That salmon sure looks mouth watering
sweet father of happy, that looks scrumptious
